    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，标题就叫\"My working day\"可以吗？然后第一个section是\"Go to work\"，里面包含哪些具体步骤呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "section Go to work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以。上班部分有三个环节：先泡茶，然后上楼，最后开始工作。泡茶对我来说很重要，给5分；上楼稍微累一点，3分；工作本身比较枯燥，1分。对了，工作的时候猫经常来打扰，所以参与者除了我还有Cat。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Do work",
        "Me",
        "Cat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，第一section已经加上：Make tea: 5: Me，Go upstairs: 3: Me，Do work: 1: Me, Cat。现在来画下班回家的部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Do work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第二个section叫\"Go home\"。下班先下楼，然后到家坐下来休息。这两步都很舒服，都给我打5分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Go home",
        "Go downstairs",
        "Sit down"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，下班部分：Go downstairs: 5: Me，然后Sit down: 5: Me。参与者都是你自己，没有Cat了对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go downstairs",
